description:
In this karaoke version of I Know Who Holds Tomorrow, we'll be singing the song with the key of A. Whether you're a seasoned karaoke singer or just starting out, this is the karaoke version for you!
If you're looking for a fun and easy way to spend your evening, this is the karaoke version for you! With lyrics that you'll love and a great performance by the cast, this is a karaoke version you'll never forget!

Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters  youtube channel.
